Sentencas: Cr-poisoning effect on pure double-perovskite PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+delta (PBSCF) cathode and La2NiO4+delta (LN)-coated PBSCF cathode is investigated.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: During the Cr poisoning test at 750 degrees C in the presence of SUS430 interconnect, the electrochemical performance of pure PBSCF cathode shows severe degradation, and the significant increase in RP is mainly contributed by the increased RL.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The BaCrO4 deposits are identified on the PBSCF cathode surface.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: LN-coated PBSCF cathode, by contrast, shows remarkable tolerance towards chromium.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The reaction between volatile Cr species and PBSCF cathode can be prevented by a dense LN coating.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thus, a more stable electrochemical performance is achieved by LN-coated cathode during the Cr poisoning test.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that the introduction of LN coating not only improves the cathode electrochemical performance, but also prevents the cathode from being poisoned by chromium.
Titulo: Promoted Cr-poisoning tolerance of La2NiO4+δ-coated PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
